		<td><b>Genesis region hacking?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I used to have a link to show how to region hack a genesis cart to play on NTSC (of a PAL game) but that board no longer seems to be in service.  Does anyone know how to do this??  Thanks

		

		</td>
	</tr>
